snippet.title: Moth Planet Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy on Steam or Itch.io
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2892590/Moth_Planet/ 
https://mothfriedgames.itch.io/moth-planet 

Moth Planet is a kinetic, energetic platformer where you play as Robin, a journalist for the "Moth Planet", seeking to uncover the mystery behind the discovery of strange ruins in the distant village of Lycosina. 

Follow Moth Fried Games:
https://mothfriedgames.neocities.org/ 
https://bsky.app/profile/mothfriedgames.bsky.social 
https://mastodon.social/@MothFriedGames 
https://twitter.com/MothFriedGames
